com.board.shape

Class Rectangle

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.board.shape.Shape
      • com.board.shape.Rectangle

  • public class Rectangle
extends Shape
    The Board Size with rectangle shape (row and column are NOT necessary to equals).
    To use this class, you must use by call getSize(int, int) or getDefaultSize().
